       <span id="ctl00_pageContent_breadCrumbs"><a target="_self" href="/archives/home/" title="">Archives</a> &gt; <a target="_self" href="/Archives/Civil_War/Civil_War_Resources_Home/" title="">Civil War Resources</a> &gt; <a target="_self" href="/Archives/Civil_War/Hunter/Hunter_s_Raid_Home/" title="">Hunter's Raid</a> &gt; <a target="_self" href="/Archives/Civil_War/Hunter/Hunter_s_Raid__Tynes_Letter/" title="<p>General David Hunter in the Shenandoah Valley, June 1864 Capt. Achilles J. Tynes Letter, June 13, 1864. General John McCausland's 5th Cavalry Brigade Hunter's Raid top level&nbsp;About this letter Captain Achilles James Tynes, CSA, wrote this letter from the Headquarters</p>">Hunter's Raid: Tynes Letter</a></span> 
